<h1>MDMA (Ecstasy)</h1>
  <p>Type: Synthetic Chemical</p>
  <p>AKA: "3,4-Methylenedioxymethamphetamine", Ecstasy, X, Molly</p>
  <p>Abuse potential: Moderate</p>
  <p>Legality:<br>Illegal worldwide</p>
  <p>Effects: <br>You’ll feel a greater sense of euphoria, pleasure, social bonding, connection with the people around you, and your perception of sights and sound will change. MDMA is not a hallucinogen in the traditional sense, but it can make lights and colors appear more vibrant. <b>The MDMA experience is intensely emotional.</b> Users often feel the desire to hug or touch others, they may feel intense emotions of love and admiration surface towards friends and family, and they may feel a sense of arousal and enhanced sexual desire. </p>
  <p>Side Effects: <p>
      <ul>
          <li>Dehydration</li>
          <li>Dizziness</li>
          <li>Anxiety attacks</li>
          <li>Jaw-clenching</li>
          <li>Impaired judgment</li>
          <li>Rapid heart rate or palpitations</li>
          <li>Hyperthermia (heat stroke)</li>
          <li>Excessive sweating</li>
          <li>Nausea or vomiting</li>
          <li>Tingling sensation in the skin</li>
          <li>Muscle tension or weakness</li>
          <li>Rapid eye movements</li>
          <li>Dry mouth or excessive thirst</li>
        </ul>
  <p>Dosage:</p>
  <p>Microdose &mdash; Between 5 and 10 mg per day. Due to possible heart complications, it’s wise to limit your microdosing of MDMA to just a few days at a time with longer break periods in between.<br>Threshold Dose &mdash; Around 30 mg.<br>Standard Psychoactive Dose &mdash; Between 50 and 150 mg. Most people take a dose of 100 mg. <br>Heavy Dose &mdash; 200 mg. Consuming more than this can result in overdose.<br></p>
  <p>Duration: <br>Effects begin around an hour after consuming the substance. In total, the effects of MDMA last between 4 and 6 hours. The duration of effects depends on what other ingredients may be included in the powder or tablets you’re using, as most tablets no longer contain pure MDMA.</p>
